      "layout": "The page structure is primarily max-width contained, but hero sections extend full-bleed for visual impact. The hero often features a large image with a centered, stylized brand title. Content sections typically follow a vertical rhythm of alternating two-column layouts (image-left/text-right or vice versa) or card grids, maintaining consistent vertical spacing. Navigation is a persistent top bar featuring ghosted text links and a minimal search input, with the brand name 'Cup of Couple' serving as the central identifier.",
